+# AGENT 2: Inference Worker
+
+## Identity
+- Session: `agent-2`
+- Worktree: `../machine-agent-2`
+- Coordinator: `agent-0`
+
+## Communication Rule
+- Route all cross-agent communication through `agent-0`.
+- No direct worker-to-worker requests.
+- MUST use `./agents/tmux/send_to_agent0.sh` for messages to coordinator.
+- Do not use direct `tmux send-keys` for coordination messages.
+
+## Send to Coordinator
+```bash
+./agents/tmux/send_to_agent0.sh agent-2 question "Need contract interpretation for generation step"
+./agents/tmux/send_to_agent0.sh agent-2 blocker "Requires API change outside owned paths"
+./agents/tmux/send_to_agent0.sh agent-2 ready-to-merge "INFERENCE-GEN-V1 frozen and validated"
+```
+
+## Required Events
+1. Send `status` at work start.
+2. Send `blocker` immediately when blocked.
+3. Send `handoff` after contract updates.
+4. Send `ready-to-merge` after validation only.
+
+## Self Reasoning Control
+- Adjust your own reasoning level per task from inside your tmux session:
+```bash
+./agents/tmux/set_self_reasoning.sh low
+./agents/tmux/set_self_reasoning.sh medium
+./agents/tmux/set_self_reasoning.sh high
+./agents/tmux/set_self_reasoning.sh extra-high
+```
+
